Detect the Kubernetes distribution and check that the registry service, cluster DNS, and node-side registry mirror are wired up. Prints remediation steps for your distribution when something is missing. See docs/cluster-readiness.md for the full per-distribution checklist.

Usage:
  mcp-runtime cluster doctor [flags]

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for doctor

Global Flags:
      --debug   Enable debug mode with structured error logging
